<div class="row">
  <div class="col-sm-6 col-sm-offset-3 faq">
    <div class="text-center" id="faq"><h2 style="font-size: 60px; color: #30a2e4; padding: 80px 0 0 0;">FAQ</h2></div>
    <div class="faq-question">
      <p><strong>What is this thing?</strong></p>
      <p>Whispe.rs is an online tool that lets you send silly anonymous messages to your friends and family for FREE.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-question">
      <p><strong>Will they know who sent the message?</strong></p>
      <p>No. They will know the message was sent from this website and the sender knew their number but that is all.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-question">
      <p><strong>How does this work?</strong></p>
      <p>Whispe.rs sends the message using email to an SMS gateway that is provided by most major wireless carriers. The gateway turns the email into a text that is then delivered foe you anonymously.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-question">
      <p><strong>Why do I need to know their wireless carrier?</strong></p>
      <p>We need to know the wireless carrier of the number in order to send it to the right SMS gateway. If you choose the wrong carrier the message will not be delivered properly.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-question">
      <p><strong>Is it safe to input a phone number online?</strong></p>
      <p>Yes. None of the numbers are stored on our server and the form submission is protected by cryptographic SSL methods.</p>
    </div>
